  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>髪の長さも違うし
性格だってまったく違うんだ。
二人は似てなんかないさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Your hair lengths are different, too,
and your personalities are totally
different. You two aren't similar at all.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうかぁ？
まぁガイがそう言うなら……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You think?
Well, if it's Guy who says so...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ったく。
素直に言う事聞くんなら
ケンカ吹っかけて来るなよな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Good lord. If you're just gonna actually
listen to him in the end anyway, don't
start fights like that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いいじゃないか。
最終的にまったく
似ていないという事になったんだから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's alright, isn't it?
You two ultimately aren't alike at all.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうそう、似てない似てない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yup, they're not alike at all.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>似てない似てない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Not at all, not at all.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うーん……お前らは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mmmm... You guys are...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
